27
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:29,629
SPEAKER_21: They're too tired. Been at it all night.

42
00:05:38,129 --> 00:05:39,459
SPEAKER_21: Take care.

131
00:14:10,409 --> 00:14:12,710
SPEAKER_21: Master Fugui, I'm sorry...

132
00:14:12,779 --> 00:14:15,769
SPEAKER_21: but you've nothing left.
What would you wager?

133
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:18,809
SPEAKER_21: If you're unhappy, talk to Mr. Xie.

145
00:15:00,620 --> 00:15:03,120
SPEAKER_21: Not that we'd accept it as ante.

146
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:06,529
SPEAKER_21: We'll formalize the transfer in a few days...

183
00:19:32,059 --> 00:19:36,660
SPEAKER_21: It's valuable. Don't scratch it. Take it slowly.

631
01:13:07,039 --> 01:13:08,670
SPEAKER_21: It's Fugui's son?

632
01:13:09,750 --> 01:13:11,649
SPEAKER_21: District Chief arrived after dark.

633
01:13:11,710 --> 01:13:16,079
SPEAKER_21: He backed up,
and his jeep knocked the wall down.

634
01:13:16,149 --> 01:13:19,020
SPEAKER_21: Youqing was sleeping on the other side.

635
01:13:19,560 --> 01:13:21,850
SPEAKER_21: When the wall collapsed...

636
01:13:22,329 --> 01:13:24,159
SPEAKER_21: he didn't have a chance.

637
01:13:24,229 --> 01:13:26,560
SPEAKER_21: The District Chief was hurt, too.

638
01:13:27,800 --> 01:13:30,130
SPEAKER_21: He hadn't slept for three days.

639
01:13:56,729 --> 01:13:58,420
SPEAKER_21: Fugui, listen to me.

640
01:13:58,489 --> 01:14:02,430
SPEAKER_21: We have to try and bear it,
even in the worst of times.

919
01:41:51,699 --> 01:41:53,890
SPEAKER_21: That she's in terrific shape.

954
01:44:16,710 --> 01:44:18,039
SPEAKER_21: Chunsheng.

955
01:44:23,149 --> 01:44:24,779
SPEAKER_21: What do you want?

956
01:44:26,949 --> 01:44:28,850
SPEAKER_21: Come out for a second.

1072
01:52:40,550 --> 01:52:41,710
SPEAKER_21: Let me think.

1149
01:59:09,670 --> 01:59:11,329
SPEAKER_21: Are they in there?

1150
01:59:11,869 --> 01:59:13,460
SPEAKER_21: - Have a look.
- Not yet!

1151
01:59:13,539 --> 01:59:15,529
SPEAKER_21: Please, I'm the father!

